ActIndian Act
SubjectAddition to Whitecap Dakota First Nation Indian Reserve No. 94, Saskatchewan
PrecisOrder setting apart 60.612 hectares (149.78 acres) of surface lands, excluding mines and minerals, for the use and benefit of the Whitecap Dakota First Nation as an addition to WHITECAP DAKOTA FIRST NATION INDIAN RESERVE NO. 94, located in the rural Municipality of Dundurn No. 314 at approximately 20 kilometres from the city of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan.
